import React from 'react'
import { View, Text, Box, Center } from 'native-base'
import Colors from '../color'

function ShippingScreen() {
  return (
    <Box flex={1} safeArea bg={Colors.main} py={5}>
      <Center>
        <Text pb={15}>
          DELIVERY ADRESS
        </Text>
      </Center>
    </Box>
  )
}

export default ShippingScreen
